genresAdvancedInfo.name: french stoner rock
genresAdvancedInfo.description: French stoner rock is a subgenre of rock music that combines heavy, distorted guitar riffs with psychedelic and bluesy elements. It is known for its slow, sludgy tempo and introspective lyrics that often touch on themes of existentialism and nihilism.
